This page is for tips and tricks about using Git with the Emacs source tree.

== Getting Emacs via Git ==

Emacs Git repositories are in a number of places. The most official one right now is savannah.

Getting Emacs via Git while using the least space:

{{{
git clone --depth 1 git://git.savannah.gnu.org/emacs.git
}}}

Getting Emacs via Git and pulling all the branches and history and what not:

{{{
git clone git://git.savannah.gnu.org/emacs.git
}}}

